<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA73">
<l>āynturaippa ṉāyirampē rātinaṭu vantivāy</l>
<l>vāynta malartūvi vaikalu – mēynta</l>
<l>piṟaikkōṭṭuc ceṅkaṭ kariviṭutta pemmā</l>
<l>ṉiṟaikkāṭ paṭattuṇinta yāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Selecting [them] I speak the thousand names, beginning, middle [and] end,</l>
<l>daily strewing available blossoms – I who decided</l>
<l>to be a servant to the lord, the great man who set free</l>
<l>the red-eyed elephant, with crescent moon tusks, he had encountered.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
